description: Miami has people coming in from all parts of the world. I feel that this place should be shared with everyone. Let's pull those people away from the stero-typical "South Beach Miami" and introduce them to a small part of the REAL Miami.Although it is known to many to be the "King of the Fritas", let's make this a place you bring one new friend or visitor every time.
name: El Rey de las Fritas
